trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.WebHttpDispatchOperationSelector> maps calls to [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] service operations based on the Uniform Resource Identifier (URI) suffix and the HTTP method used.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.WebHttpDispatchOperationSelector>mappar anrop till [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] tjänsten åtgärder baserat på suffixet identifierare URI (Uniform Resource) och HTTP-metod som används.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.WebHttpDispatchOperationSelector>

trans-unit.source: This is an extensibility point that derived behaviors can use to supply their own implementation of <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.WebHttpDispatchOperationSelector> that maps the incoming HTTP request to a service operation.
trans-unit.target: Det här är en utökningspunkt som härletts beteenden kan använda för att ange sina egna implementering av <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.WebHttpDispatchOperationSelector>som mappar inkommande HTTP-begäran till en tjänståtgärd.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.WebHttpDispatchOperationSelector>

trans-unit.source: To enable the helpEnabled attribute in a configuration file: ``` <system.serviceModel> <behaviors> <endpointBehaviors> <behavior name="MyEndpointBehavior"> <webHttp helpEnabled="true" /> </behavior> </endpointBehaviors> </system.serviceModel> ``` To programmatically enable the HelpEnabled property: ``` WebHttpBehavior helpBehavior = new WebHttpBehavior(); helpBehavior.HelpEnabled = true; host.Description.Endpoints[0].Behaviors.Add(helpBehavior); ```
trans-unit.target: Så här aktiverar du helpEnabled-attributet i en konfigurationsfil: ``` <system.serviceModel> <behaviors> <endpointBehaviors> <behavior name="MyEndpointBehavior"> <webHttp helpEnabled="true" /> </behavior> </endpointBehaviors> </system.serviceModel> ``` programmässigt aktivera egenskapen HelpEnabled:``` WebHttpBehavior helpBehavior = new WebHttpBehavior(); helpBehavior.HelpEnabled = true; host.Description.Endpoints[0].Behaviors.Add(helpBehavior); ```

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Help page is enabled; otherwise <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.

trans-unit.target: Kontrollerar du följande:-slutpunkten är inte `null`.

trans-unit.source: - The endpoint uses the HTTP or HTTPS schemes.
trans-unit.target: -Slutpunkten använder HTTP eller HTTPS-scheman.

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MessageVersion> of the binding is set to <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MessageVersion.None%2A>.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MessageVersion>Om bindningen är inställd på <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MessageVersion.None%2A>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MessageVersion.None%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MessageVersion>

trans-unit.source: - The binding contains an <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.HttpTransportBindingElement> where <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TransportBindingElement.ManualAddressing%2A> is set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: -Bindningen innehåller ett <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.HttpTransportBindingElement>där <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TransportBindingElement.ManualAddressing%2A>är inställd på `true`.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TransportBindingElement.ManualAddressing%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.HttpTransportBindingElement>

trans-unit.source: - The parameters specified in the <xref:System.UriTemplate> must be part of the operation.
trans-unit.target: -De angivna parametrarna i den <xref:System.UriTemplate>måste vara en del av åtgärden.</xref:System.UriTemplate>
